"}, "is_active": true, "auto_gradable": true, "difficulty": 3, "explanation": null}, {"id": "cap-105-chinese-048", "exam_id": "cap", "subject_id": "sub-cap-chinese", "paper_id": "cap-105-chinese", "question_type": "single_choice", "question_text": "根據本文內容，下列敘述何者正確？", "options": ["次仲因擅自改革文字觸怒始皇，而遭逮捕", "始皇過於急功好利，故次仲出走轉而修道", "次仲將篆籀之體改為隸書，方便世人使用", "仙鳥中始皇之箭，落羽成大翮、小翮二山 13               試題結束"], "correct_answer": 2, "correct_answer_json": null, "parent_question_id": "cap-105-chinese-passage-47", "media": null, "source": "official", "source_meta": {"parser_version": "cap_v0.1", "merger_version": "cap_merger_v0.2", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T19:26:37+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "9643cac0c05a", "answer_pdf_sha1": "e4e2292682e2", "flags": [], "parse_confidence": 1.0, "original_question_number": 48, "raw_text": "48.    根據本文內容，下列敘述何者正確？\n      (A)次仲因擅自改革文字觸怒始皇，而遭逮捕\n      (B)始皇過於急功好利，故次仲出走轉而修道\n      (C)次仲將篆籀之體改為隸書，方便世人使用\n      (D)仙鳥中始皇之箭，落羽成大翮、小翮二山\n\n\n\n\n                         13               試題結束\n"}, "is_active": true, "auto_gradable": true, "difficulty": 3, "explanation": null}]'::jsonb) AS t(
